# Architectural Refactoring: LLM Service Layer & Batch Embeddings

Improve the application architecture and API efficiency by introducing a dedicated LLM Service layer, batching embedding requests, and optimizing chat session state.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The new design transitions chat history from stateful Gemini Chat objects (`gc.chats.create`) to stateless prompt completions (`gc.models.generate_content`). 
> This is cleaner and faster because conversation history is already managed database-side and passed down on each request.

> [!TIP]
> Batching embeddings will group chunk uploads together, reducing the time required to index PDFs and significantly reducing API request overhead.

